###
# XVC Interview API — REST Client Demo
# 安装 VS Code "REST Client" 插件后，点击每段请求上方的 "Send Request" 即可测试
###

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8787
@videoUrl = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xRh2sVcNXQ8

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Extract YouTube Subtitles
# 纯网络爬取，无需 API Key
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subtitles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoUrl": "{{videoUrl}}"
}

### 3. Stream Generate Article
# 流式输出，Response 为 chunked text/plain
# 需配置有效的 GEMINI_API_KEY（.dev.vars 或 wrangler secret）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "xRh2sVcNXQ8",
  "subtitles": "Marc Andreessen discusses AI revenue models and cost curves with Ben Horowitz."
}

### 4. Stream Generate with Requirements
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "xRh2sVcNXQ8",
  "subtitles": "Marc Andreessen discusses AI revenue models and cost curves with Ben Horowitz.",
  "requirements": "{\"taskType\":\"深度分析\",\"style\":\"正式\",\"audience\":\"投资人\"}"
}

### 5. Summarize Chapter 5W1H
# 先执行 generate 获取返回的 sessionId，替换下方 {{sessionId}}
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/summarize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "replace-with-session-id-from-generate-response",
  "chapterIndex": 0
}
